content:
DUBAI: Saeed Mohammed Al Tayer, MD and CEO of Dubai Electricity and Water Authority (Dewa), welcomed at his office Emmanuel Kamarianakis, Consul General of Canada to Dubai, and Glen McPherson, Consul and Senior Trade Commissioner in the Consulate General of Canada to Dubai, as part of a series of diplomatic and consular visits to Dewa.
